# Mutable content at stable URLs — HTML, the kernel + lattice JS, the share card —
# must revalidate at the edge so a repaint or a takedown propagates immediately
# instead of lingering behind a long edge TTL (the gold-palette / orrery hazard).
# There are NO content-hashed immutable assets on this site (all JS/PNG are
# fixed-name and mutable); if any are ever added under a content hash, give them
# a more-specific long-TTL rule ABOVE this one.
/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate
